                  <h3 class="title">ENERGY HARVESTER</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-6 col-xs-12">
                      <p class="pd-font">A wide range of wireless devices has been manufactured that become very important to normal consumer, industrial and military needs. Unfortunately, with existing technology, wireless devices are constrained by their inability to operate under independent of centralized power sources for a long duration. As a result, the usefulness of wireless devices, is severely restricted by relatively slow advancements in rechargeable battery technology. A clear market need exist that either allows wireless devices to operate for longer durations away from centralised power sources or increases the amount of power that can be supplied to a wireless device. So, that energy harvesting will only be a new technology that is going to make a revolution in the coming decade.</p>
