                  <h3 class="title">Industry best</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-6 col-xs-12">
                <p class="pd-font">
                  Bluesemi have proven prototypes of Multi Self Sustaining Energy Harvesters with a wide range of reception and running at Ultra Low Power based on Sub Threshold technology. We have Self Powered low headroom sub threshold designs along with Narrow band filters with tuning capability.Higher average current load delivery capability with a wider coverage up to 2 meters and High thermal to electrical conversion ratio. Our system can handle a load of upto 25 mA for a duration suitable for bluetooth and wifi communications and can provide an average current of upto 500 uA making it most suitable for smart wearables, wireless sensor network and real time tracking devices.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="col-lg-6">
                <ul class="zpiz_ul">
                  <h3 class="text-center">Features</h3>
                  <li>High ambient reception radius of more than 2 mts.</li>
                  <li>Best Load Capability of 180mw.</li>
                  <li>Ultra low stand by power of 1 nW.</li>
                  <li>Least foot print of 0.1 sq. mm.</li>
                  <li>Supports a wide supply range of 0.5 V - 3.3 V.</li>
                  <li>Wide Temperature range of -55 deg C to 125 deg C.</li>
                  <li>Multi band tuning capability.</li>
